Nigeria’s Sterling Bank Agrees to Buy Equitorial Trust Bank, Vanguard Says

-- B y   E l i s h a   B a l a - G b o g b o
-- 
2011-08-12T07:28:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-12/nigeria-s-sterling-bank-agrees-to-buy-equitorial-trust-bank-vanguard-says.html
Sterling Bank (STERLNBA)  Plc of  Nigeria  signed
an agreement to buy Equitorial Trust Bank Plc, a Lagos-based
lender bailed out by Nigeria’s central bank in 2009, Vanguard
reported, citing a statement from Sterling Bank.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Elisha Bala-Gbogbo in Abuja at 
 ebalagbogbo@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
